      "beast_baseline": "hey im stuck on this ac circuit problem for class. i have a series circuit with a 120V source at 60Hz. there is a 50 ohm resistor and an inductor with an inductive reactance of 30 ohms. can you help me find the total impedance and the total current in the circuit? thanks",
